originalText.text: The best doctor I've ever had the pleasure of receiving care from. She's everything we could have hoped for during our pregnancy. She's kind and funny and informative and never judgemental and open and considerate and an amazing caregiver. I'd give ten stars if I could.

originalText.text:
I cannot overstate how grateful I am to Dr. Meisler for her warm attention and thorough care over the course of my pregnancy, before my pregnancy, and during the birth of my son earlier this summer. I look forward to being a patient of hers for many years to come!

In addition, my husband and I had the most awesome experience delivering at Weill Cornell. Along with Dr. Meisler - who we were fortunate enough to have deliver our baby - our PAs, nurses, and anesthesiologists were amazing, as was every member of every team we interacted with.

Five glowing stars for Dr. Meisler! I highly recommend working with her if you are fortunate enough to be able to.
